 in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/jordanpass\/\" target=\"_blank\">Jordan Pass online<\/a>. The Jordan Explorer includes your visa to Jordan (usually 40 JOD), a 2-day entrance to Petra, and 40 other big attractions in Jordan. The costs are 75 JOD (~ 105 USD).<br><br><strong>Important: <\/strong>Take your passport, you have to show this with your ticket at the entrance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/viewpoint-petra-jordan.jpg\" alt=\"viewpoint petra jordan\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"313\" alt=\"viewpoint petra jordan\" class=\"wp-image-13314 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140802\/viewpoint-petra-jordan.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140802\/viewpoint-petra-jordan-300x209.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140802\/viewpoint-petra-jordan-600x418.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140802\/viewpoint-petra-jordan-450x313.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140802\/viewpoint-petra-jordan-800x557.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140802\/viewpoint-petra-jordan-1080x752.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140802\/viewpoint-petra-jordan-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140802\/viewpoint-petra-jordan-163x113.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140802\/viewpoint-petra-jordan-259x180.jpg 259w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140802\/viewpoint-petra-j