use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/book-jordan-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Book your tour online (opens in a new tab)\">Book your tour online<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"hotels\">Hotels in Petra<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>All hotels in Petra are in Wadi Musa, a perfect location at the entrance of Petra. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Hotels in Petra: <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/petra-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Find all hotels<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/petra-guesthouse\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140906\/176438837-30x17.jpg\" alt=\"Bedouin Garden Guesthouse\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/23140906\/176438837-450x253.jpg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">